definition: to exchange/to change (clothes etc)/to substitute/to switch/to convert (currency)

sentences.english: This is a Desert Wheatear for me, a fresh female.
sentences.chinese: 我認爲這是一隻剛換羽的漠即鳥母鳥。

sentences.english: Looks like a worn and moulting Arctic Warbler.
sentences.chinese: 看起來像是隻羽毛磨損且正換羽中的極北柳鶯。

sentences.english: The moulting process happens to the adult birds as well as the young penguins.
sentences.chinese: 成年鳥類和小企鵝都會經歷換羽過程。
